data.description: Welcome to your MOVE-IN READY home!  Within a few minutes of downtown Raleigh and historical parks, nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, this cozy home greets you with a bonus room with sliding double barn doors, upgraded granite kitchen with tile flooring & SS appliances! This Craftsman style home has LVP throughout!  Holidays will be filled with memories with crown molding trim coupled with a log-burning fireplace.  On the second floor, the owner's suite boasts space suited for a California King accompanied with owner's en-suite and walk-in closet. The laundry room, conveniently located along the main hallway, leads to the bedrooms and full bath on the far side of the home.  Although, the HOA approved the screened-in porch and fence, it does not have a permit on record with the city.  The enlarged yard space extends beyond the fence line.  This home is equipped with a new HVAC, new layer of shingle and solar panels.  Solar panels will convey with the property and the corresponding loan will be paid off in full at or before closing.  HOA fees only $25/mo! Seller offers 10k to use as you choose!
